### ============================================================
### 2. USUARIOS - CRUD (GET/DELETE)
### ============================================================

### 2.1 Obtener todos los usuarios (solo ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}
### 2.2 Obtener usuario por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

### 2.3 Eliminar usuario por ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### ============================================================
### 3. REPORTES - CRUD
### ============================================================

### 3.1 Crear nuevo reporte
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reports
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "title": "Perro herido en el parque",
  "description": "Se encuentra un perro pequeño con una herida en la pata delantera",
  "latitude": 40.4168,
  "longitude": -3.7038,
  "address": "Parque del Retiro, Madrid",
  "animalType": "dog",
  "animalCondition": "injured",
  "animalDescription": "Perro blanco y marrón, aproximadamente 5kg"
}

### 3.2 Obtener todos los reportes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reports
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### 3.3 Obtener reporte por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### 3.4 Obtener reportes por usuario
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/user/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### 3.5 Obtener reportes por estado
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/status/OPEN
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### 3.6 Obtener reportes cercanos (geolocalización)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/nearby?latitude=40.4168&longitude=-3.7038&radiusKm=5
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### 3.7 Actualizar estado del reporte
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/1/status
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "newStatus": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### 3.8 Eliminar reporte
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### ============================================================
### 4. CREAR MÚLTIPLES REPORTES (Para probar geolocalización)
### ============================================================

### 4.1 Reporte 2 - Gato en calle
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reports
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "title": "Gato perdido",
  "description": "Gato gris desaparecido hace 3 días",
  "latitude": 40.4201,
  "longitude": -3.7036,
  "address": "Calle Príncipe, Madrid",
  "animalType": "cat",
  "animalCondition": "lost",
  "animalDescription": "Gato gris con collar rojo"
}

### 4.2 Reporte 3 - Pájaro herido
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reports
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "title": "Pájaro herido en el suelo",
  "description": "Pájaro que no puede volar",
